Hi,
On Wed, Mar 29, 2000 at 01:31:25PM +0530, Raju K V wrote:
> 
> Is the b_size field of buffer_head same as the block size of the
> filesystem?
Usually.  It's the block size of the buffer.  Filesystems set the
device's block size when they first start up, usually.
